	 (2000000088,2000000000,'I am a 35-year-old male patient, and I have been experiencing shortness of breath, chest pain, and fatigue. I was referred to Dr. Walker by my primary care physician due to these symptoms. My primary care physician mentioned that there might be an underlying heart condition, and I wanted to discuss this with Dr. Walker.','2023-02-24 13:00:00'),
	 (2000000086,2000000001,'As an adult patient, my consult concerns persistent hip pain that has limited my daily activities for the past three months. I am looking to discuss various treatment options, including medication, physical therapy, and potential surgery, to alleviate the pain and restore my quality of life.','2023-08-02 14:00:00'),
