	 (2000000081,2000000002,'Hello Doctor Gilbert, I have been experiencing sudden and severe headaches accompanied by sensitivity to light. I have also noticed changes in my mood and difficulty concentrating. These symptoms have been ongoing for about a week now, and I am quite concerned. Can you please examine me and run some tests to determine the underlying cause?','2023-02-22 12:00:00'),
	 (2000000082,2000000002,'I have been experiencing headaches and dizziness lately, and I was wondering if these symptoms might be related to a neurological issue. As a former athlete, I''ve also been having trouble with my balance and coordination. I''m just wondering if these symptoms could be related to each other, or if there might be something more serious going on.','2023-05-02 13:00:00'),
