	 (2000000083,2000000004,'I am consulting Dr. Miller regarding persistent abdominal pain and bloating, frequent bowel movements, and changes in my diet and weight. I am also experiencing nausea and fatigue that have been going on for the past few weeks.','2023-05-31 13:00:00'),
	 (2000000085,2000000004,'Dear Doctor Miller, I am an adult patient with recurring abdominal pain and discomfort. Can it be related to my gastrointestinal system? If so, how can we proceed in determining the underlying cause?','2023-06-06 12:00:00'),
