	 (2000000081,2000000005,'I am an adult patient seeking consultation with Doctor Garcia, a renowned Dermatologist. I would like to discuss my recent changes in skin pigmentation, which I believe might be related to an underlying medical condition. Additionally, I would like to learn about possible treatment options and preventative measures to maintain the health of my skin.','2023-03-01 14:00:00'),
	 (2000000084,2000000005,'I would like to discuss my persistent rash on my face that has been causing cosmetic concerns, as well as some other dermatological issues.','2023-07-27 13:00:00'),
