	 (2000000084,2000000006,'Doctor Miller, I''ve been experiencing headaches and dizziness lately, and I was wondering if these symptoms could be related to my thyroid, as I''ve heard that it can affect hormonal balance. I''m also a little concerned about my overall energy levels, as I''ve been feeling a bit fatigued lately. Could you provide me with some insight into these symptoms, and if so, what tests or examinations I should undergo? Thank you.','2023-07-17 12:00:00'),
	 (2000000085,2000000006,'As an adult patient, I am concerned about my overall health and well-being, and I am seeking advice from Dr. Miller, a pediatric specialist. My main concern is managing chronic pain and fatigue that have been ongoing for the past few months. I have also been experiencing frequent headaches and difficulty sleeping, which exacerbates my existing issues. Can Dr. Miller provide any insights or solutions for these problems? I am open to exploring medication or alternative therapies, and I value the doctor''s expertise in this field.','2023-07-17 14:00:00');
