	 (2000000082,2000000007,'Hello Doctor Carter, I am concerned about my urinary issues, particularly difficulty urinating and frequent urination. Could you provide some insights into what could be causing this problem and recommend any treatment options? Thank you.','2023-01-10 12:00:00'),
	 (2000000087,2000000007,'Dear Dr. Carter, I am a 40-year-old male experiencing urinary frequency and discomfort during urination, which has been ongoing for the past 6 months. Could you please provide some information on the possible causes and potential treatments for these symptoms, as well as any diagnostic tests that may be required? Thank you.','2023-08-10 13:00:00'),
