	 (2000000083,2000000008,'As a 45-year-old patient, I am concerned about my recent difficulty seeing clearly. The last few months, it has become increasingly difficult to focus and I''m finding it hard to read or see fine details. I''m wondering if this could be related to age or if it could be a sign of something more serious.','2023-03-16 13:00:00'),
	 (2000000082,2000000009,'Hello, my name is Ana. I recently experienced chest pain and shortness of breath, and was advised by my primary care physician to schedule an appointment with a cardiologist. I am eager to learn what might be the cause of my symptoms and what the available treatment options might be. Can you provide me with some guidance on what questions to ask during our consultation?','2023-05-18 13:00:00'),
