	 (2000000088,2000000033,'As a concerned adult patient, I would like to discuss my overall health concerns and recent changes in my wellbeing. I have been experiencing fatigue, unexplained weight gain, and have noticed decreased energy levels. I believe these symptoms could be related to an underlying medical condition.','2023-01-23 13:00:00'),
	 (2000000084,2000000034,'As a patient, I am consulting Doctor Hill, a specialist in Urology regarding my urinary tract problems. I am experiencing frequent urination and pain during urination, and I am concerned about the possible underlying cause. I would like Doctor Hill to examine my medical history, conduct a physical examination, and provide any necessary tests or procedures to determine the cause of my issues.','2023-01-05 13:00:00'),
