	 (2000000087,2000000035,'I am a middle-aged adult who has been experiencing blurry vision and difficulty seeing in dim lighting. I have also been experiencing eye strain and headaches. Doctor Smith, can you help me diagnose the root cause of these symptoms?','2023-02-15 12:00:00'),
