	 (2000000086,2000000036,'I am a 40-year-old patient, and I am experiencing shortness of breath, chest discomfort, and fatigue, which I believe might be related to some underlying heart condition. Can you provide me with information on the types of tests and procedures that may be necessary to diagnose the issue and determine the best course of action for treatment? Thank you.','2023-05-10 12:00:00');
