	 (2000000082,2000000038,'Today, I am experiencing muscle twitches, stiffness, and weakness in my arms, legs, and neck. They are interfering with my daily activities and are affecting my quality of life. I am also having difficulty with balance and coordination, which is making it difficult for me to walk without aid. I have a family history of neurological diseases, and I am concerned that these symptoms may be related.','2023-06-27 13:00:00'),
