	 (2000000085,2000000039,'As an adult patient, my primary concern is cancer prevention and early detection. My medical history includes a family history of cancer, and I recently experienced abdominal pain which may or may not be related. I would like Doctor Roberts'' opinion on whether these symptoms warrant further examination or screening to reduce the risk of potential cancer.','2023-01-09 12:00:00'),
	 (2000000088,2000000039,'Dear Doctor Roberts, during my recent physical examination, I noticed a lump on my abdomen which has been a constant discomfort to me. Could you please assess the lump and provide an opinion whether it might be something serious or not? Thank you.','2023-02-16 12:00:00');
