	 (2000000088,2000000040,'I am a 45-year-old male who has been experiencing abdominal pain and bloating after meals for the past several weeks. Other symptoms include nausea, heartburn, and diarrhea. Doctor Miller, I am concerned about the possible causes and treatments for these symptoms.','2023-02-01 14:00:00'),
